INFO:

You just downloaded your favourite software and you are ready to
install it. Before you install it you start keygen program because you are so
bad ass pirate >). Suddenly your head start nodding. What a hell is
happening to me - you ask? The catchy tune in keygen program is drilling 
inside your head and you start waving your head like discomaniac. 
Goddaam this is on groovy tune!! ..and these groovy tunes is what this 
compilation is all about. 41 catchy poppy chiptune electronica tracks 
for your pleasure and pain. We old school nerds call them trackker music. >)

Some nice fellow uploaded massive collection of these keygen tunes in various 
trackker format. I just collected the best of them and converted them
to mp3 format. I also added scene tags most of them. There is also 
orginal collection. You can use modplug player to play them. <a href="
http://www.modplug.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.modplug.com/</a>


Feel Free to Comment! =)
